#~ msgctxt "worst_case"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Modern Health goes on to say they can use information they collect on you to target you with personalized ads, send you marketing information, and conduct research. They also say they can share your"
#~ " personal information with a number of third parties, including business affiliates and your employer. Modern Health doesn’t specifically state in their privacy policy that they don’t sell user "
#~ "data, which is something we like to see stated clearly. That's not a good thing to be unclear on."
